46
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:21,803
Fleshlumpeater, Bonecruncher, Manhugger...

47
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:27,649
Childchewer, Meatdripper, Gizzardgulper, Maidmasher...

48
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:29,205
Blood bottler.

49
