- Run, Sophie! Run!

884
01:42:56,080 --> 01:42:58,401
It's over, Fleshlumpeater.

885
01:42:59,040 --> 01:43:01,202
It's over, boy.

886
01:43:01,360 --> 01:43:03,044
It's time to stop now.

887
01:43:05,320 --> 01:43:07,402
I's always hungry.

888
01:43:11,440 --> 01:43:12,566
Huh?

889
01:43:17,160 --> 01:43:18,525
Whoa!

