923
01:48:06,080 --> 01:48:09,801
<i>He was happy, and I was happy.</i>

924
01:48:10,920 --> 01:48:14,481
<i>When I'm lonely, which is not nearly as often as before,</i>

925
01:48:15,080 --> 01:48:18,368
